{"tha-ap555:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap555:0.2":"Yasavagga ","tha-ap555:0.3":"Gayakassapattheraapadana ","tha-ap555:1.1":"“Ajinacammavatthoham, ","tha-ap555:1.2":"kharibharadharo tada; ","tha-ap555:1.3":"Kharikam harayitvana, ","tha-ap555:1.4":"kolam ahasi assamam. ","tha-ap555:2.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap555:2.2":"eko adutiyo jino; ","tha-ap555:2.3":"Mamassamam upagacchi, ","tha-ap555:2.4":"jotento sabbakalikam. ","tha-ap555:3.1":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap555:3.2":"abhivadetvana subbatam; ","tha-ap555:3.3":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap555:3.4":"kolam buddhassadasaham. ","tha-ap555:4.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap555:4.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap555:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap555:4.4":"koladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap555:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap555:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap555:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap555:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap555:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap555:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap555:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap555:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap555:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap555:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma gayakassapo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap555:9.1":"Gayakassapattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}